title: Moobala Schmoobala
description: Moobala Schmoobala is a big-hearted, fun-loving alien (ET) from the planet Googala. He and his kooky best friend, Boobala, visit Earth and have tons of fun traveling the globe meeting lots of new animal friends along the way. An artful, educational rhyming children's picture book.
author: M.G. Wells
